parameters:
We have no choice but to focus on these four...
and proceed with caution.

If we can quietly observe the suspicious behavior
of these four individuals within \C[2] hours and
gather evidence, we might have a chance! The key
lies in Pian's reaction and the movements of the
person. If only we had that skill possessed by
LoliMon...?

Identify the culprit within 1 minute time limit
and catch them! Ready...

What's going on? Did you lose all your money and
even your clothes?

JP is the best after all! The negotiations are
exquisite and amazing.

Hahaha! Even if you dress like that, I won't give
you any tips.

Wow, winning day after day! I guess this is what
they mean by having an easy talent.
If you take a seat, you can play anytime ♪
If you take a seat, you can play anytime ♪
If you take a seat, you can play anytime ♪

Well... Lately, I've been having a bit of
trouble... during the game...

It's difficult to say, but I've been troubled by
being groped... I can't concentrate during the
game...

What's that!? But if I know who the other person
is...!

I don't know what kind of method it is, but even
when there's no one around... I feel like I'm
being touched in various ways...

How malicious. I don't know what it is, but it
must be some kind of magic...

But it's a problem if even the security guards
haven't noticed...

If it's possible, I would be grateful if you could
find the culprit... Could you please help me
somehow...?

Of course, can you leave it to me? I'll somehow
find a way to squeeze out the culprit...!

Thank you very much! Konoha-san, please stand
behind me at a good timing.
I'm sorry, but I'm a little busy right now...

Konoha-san, please stand behind me at a good
timing!

I'm sorry, I completely let them escape... without
presenting any evidence...

I-I see... hah... hah... ♥ If things continue like
this... it seems like it'll become a habit...
Please take responsibility...

I caught the culprit~ It was an outrageous
pervert, wasn't it?

Thank you very much, Konoha-san! With this, I can
focus on the game...!

Ah... Konoha-san, would you like to play JP with
me sometime? (Ah... it reminds me of that time I
was groped...)

Hey, sis, you're dressed in an interesting
outfit, huh? But I won't be fooled, you know? If
someone messes with you, a scary big brother will
show up later, right? I know that.

I'm doing pretty well today, playing it safe and
winning a bit. You know, I tend to lose quickly
when I get carried away, so I better be careful.
I always carefully consider when to stop playing~

Hey, sis, you should take better care of your
body!

Haah! This is no good, no good at all!!! I can't
win at all!!!! Aaaaaahhhhh! My entire fortune!!!!

Hey, what are you doing? This isn't that kind of
place, you know. It's a wholesome gambling
establishment, so don't get the wrong idea.

I'm here to earn money and get some good
equipment...!!!

Just because you take off your clothes, it doesn't
mean your luck will return... Seriously, what a
fool.

If you calmly get in bed, you should be able to
win properly. Just make sure not to get greedy.

Hey, did you get taken down by the enemy? Not just
your outfit, but your head too, right?

If you're no longer satisfied with the stakes
here... there are even more amazing places... of
course, the risks are higher though.

We are monitoring to ensure there is no
misconduct.

We are monitoring to ensure there is no
misconduct.

We are monitoring to ensure there is no
misconduct.

Haha! What's the matter? Did you lose, by any
chance?

It seems like my luck has been turning around
lately. I've managed to make quite a bit of money
and occasionally have some cozy time
underground...

I approached from the front, so they became
cautious!
(As for the suspicious part in my hands...)
(I have a feeling that's not right...)

Huh? What's this all about? I haven't done
anything. There's no evidence either.
